


Feature
1 - hg flow feature start myfeature
2 - hg flow feature finish myfeature

3 - hg flow release start myRelease
    hg flow release publish myRelease
4 - hg flow release finish myRelease 
    hg push --tags

if something went bad you always can revert
hg update --clean

Hotfix
1 - hg flow hotgix start myHotfix
2 - hg flow hitfix finish myHotfix

